itunes:title: Big Pimpin', Trendin' G's 8/1:Nichelle Nichols, Bill Russell, Pat Carroll, Mexican Pizza, Music Midtown Festival, Zahara Jolie-Pitt, Mirror City, Elon Musk
description:
In this edition of Trendin' G's, Miles and super producer Becca discuss the passings of Pat Carroll, Nichelle Nichols and Bill Russell, the return of the Mexican Pizza, the Music Midtown Festival being cancelled because guns are more important, Zahara Jolie-Pitt heading off to Spelman, the Saudi 'Mirror City' concept, and Elon Musks' shitty, disapproving dad!
